{"tid":1988054,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"以香港做場景的視覺小說《A Summer's End - Hong Kong 1986》","createTime":"2020-04-25T02:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T20:14:06.000Z","uid":321748,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fa2874bade080b29f6733b92fd761d77a6b85a75","tid":1988054,"uid":321748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:41:41.000Z","msg":"新一個以香港做場景的視覺小說《A Summer's End - Hong Kong 1986》剛於本周推出。這小說透過描述兩個女子於一九八六年香港的邂逅，探討大家可以怎樣做，才能在這個文化及意見紛陳的世界中尋求自身的定位。大家在細讀其故事主線之餘,亦不妨留意當中的細節，有不少與香港文化有關。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ib7Mef7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fib7Mef7.png&h=8ed545a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37067bbf5755361d3a65229772f5585be1f1419b","tid":1988054,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:47:35.000Z","msg":"d art幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f219c4b13c755aeec37e9392dc6cc965f88757","tid":1988054,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:54:24.000Z","msg":"估唔到有鬼佬整香港game"},{"pid":"6d9f10b521fecc731f1bfbac2854f5a132564ae7","tid":1988054,"uid":321748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T20:14:06.000Z","msg":"其實外國人一直都在把香港加入去佢哋的 Game 。近兩年就有 The Hong Kong Massacre 、Phantom Doctrine 、Trials: Rising 等等。<br />\n這一隻我覺得驚喜之處，是見到各種各樣地道的香港文化穿插其中，沒有一定心思搜集資料並串連資料，不會做得到。"}]}